    • ready → editable
    • assigned → structure locked
    • archived → hidden
    • deprecated → excluded from future comparisons

13️⃣ RANDOMIZATION AT ASSIGNMENT LEVEL
Important separation.
Template contains fixed question set.
At assignment stage:
Teacher may enable:
Shuffle Question Order = ON/OFF
This:
    • Shuffles display order
    • Does NOT change canonicalId
    • Does NOT change structural identity
    • Does NOT affect analytics normalization
Each session stores:
displayOrderMap
Ensures fairness.

14️⃣ TEMPLATE ANALYTICS
Cross-run evaluation.
All metrics must use:
    • Avg Raw Score %
    • Avg Accuracy %
    • Never raw marks.
L1:
    • Avg Raw %
    • Avg Accuracy %
    • Run count
L2:
    • Phase adherence variance
    • Risk distribution shift
    • Stability variance
    • Discipline stress score
    • Controlled vs Uncontrolled delta
All aggregated in:
templateAnalytics/{testId}
Never recompute from sessions on read.

15️⃣ DISTRIBUTION REVIEW
Displays:
    • Difficulty %
    • Chapter coverage
    • Marks distribution
    • Section balance
L2 adds:
    • Estimated stress index
    • Phase load preview
    • Risk prediction preview
Purely structural view.

