No session data embedded.

17️⃣ HOT–WARM–COLD MODEL
HOT:
Templates used current year.
WARM:
Templates unused but recent.
COLD:
Unused > 2 years.
Metadata retained.
Images may move to archive bucket.
Never delete template with historical runs.

18️⃣ SECURITY RULES
    • Students never access template directly.
    • Session always references templateId.
    • Structural fields locked post-assignment.
    • Mode capability cannot be downgraded post-assignment.

19️⃣ PERFORMANCE RULES
Never:
    • Query sessions inside Tests section.
    • Compute distribution dynamically.
    • Rebuild canonicalId on read.
Always:
    • Store difficultyDistribution snapshot.
    • Store question count snapshot.
    • Increment totalRuns via atomic counter.

